                        "version": 0,
                        "content": "A client with a chest injury has suffered flail chest. The nurse assesses the client for which most distinctive sign of flail chest?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "11797937e327eb6d913faa80427c566b",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Analyzing 分析",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nFlail chest results from multiple rib fractures. This results in a \"floating\" section of ribs. Because this section is unattached to the rest of the bony rib cage, this segment results in paradoxical chest movement. This means that the force of inspiration pulls the fractured segment inward, while the rest of the chest expands. Similarly, during exhalation, the segment balloons outward while the rest of the chest moves inward. This is a characteristic sign of flail chest.",
                        "id": "87877e12dc304c59849770c76dd7d532",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "63ed2513619c4fceb86d5fd1051359a4",
                                "content": "Just under the left clavicle"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "1ca7ba9f1e9b4402bd7f167fb66554ae",
                                "content": "Midsternum, 1 inch to the left"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "e8eeb1cc3b2f44d0ae6b8e218c37afaf",
                                "content": "Over the fifth intercostal space"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "7a5d3f5904c44fb4aeb1356252b59404",
                                "content": "Midsternum, 1 inch to the right"
                            }
                        ],
                        "extJson": {
                            "optionList": [
                                {
                                    "isRight": "1",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "63ed2513619c4fceb86d5fd1051359a4",
                                    "content": "Just under the left clavicle"
                                },
                                {
                                    "isRight": "0",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "1ca7ba9f1e9b4402bd7f167fb66554ae",
                                    "content": "Midsternum, 1 inch to the left"
                                },
                                {
                                    "isRight": "0",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "e8eeb1cc3b2f44d0ae6b8e218c37afaf",
                                    "content": "Over the fifth intercostal space"
                                },
                                {
                                    "isRight": "0",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "7a5d3f5904c44fb4aeb1356252b59404",
                                    "content": "Midsternum, 1 inch to the right"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        "isSubmit": "0",
