                        "type": "0",
                        "version": 0,
                        "content": "The emergency department nurse is assessing a client who has sustained a blunt injury to the chest wall. Which finding indicates the presence of a pneumothorax in this client?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "11797937e327eb6d913faa80427c566b",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Analyzing 分析",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nThis client has sustained a blunt or closed-chest injury. Basic symptoms of a closed pneumothorax are shortness of breath and chest pain. A larger pneumothorax may cause tachypnea, cyanosis, diminished breath sounds, and subcutaneous emphysema. Hyperresonance also may occur on the affected side. A sucking sound at the site of injury would be noted with an open chest injury.",
                        "id": "a14ccff0c99f4426ad65a668d7e7af59",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "c0f69d10e55047e4850e1c3c3fab38a4",
                                "content": "I will lie on the affected side for an hour."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "fdda5411edd84073a765bc335471d0ae",
                                "content": "I can expect a chest x-ray exam to be done shortly."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "a018bd192a3a446a94716cd940e60590",
                                "content": "I will let you know at once if I have trouble breathing."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "75d9c75a967845ef86c3e03b36074f9c",
                                "content": "I will notify you if I feel a crackling sensation in my chest."
                            }
                        ],
                        "extJson": {
                            "optionList": [
